      by Alan Furst</a></strong></p>
      <p align="left" class="style73"><a href="ESL.English.Learning.Audiobooks/ESL.English.Learning.Audiobooks.html">Night Soldiers re-creates the European world of 1934–45: the struggle between Nazi Germany and Soviet Russia for Eastern Europe, the last desperate gaiety of the beau monde in 1937 Paris, and guerrilla operations with the French underground in 1944. Night Soldiers is a panoramic novel, a work on a grand scale.</a></p>
      
    <td width="16%" height="291" valign="top"><div align="center">
