      <strong>by Isaac Asimov</strong></a></p>
      <p align="left" class="style73"><a href="Novellas.for.ESL.Students/Novellas.for.ESL.html">Andrew is an super intelligent human-like robot. And Andrew's goal is to become fully human and to be granted full legal status as a human. However, before he can achieve that pinnacle, he first must arrange for his &quot;natural death.&quot; It is a compelling story of what it means to be human as well as how humans interact with each other and face their fears of other intellects.</a>   </p>
      
