      </a><a href="ESL.English.Listening.Short.Stories/ESL.Listening.Short.Stories.html"><strong>by Frederick Forsyth</strong></a></p>
      <p align="left" class="style73"><a href="ESL.English.Listening.Short.Stories/ESL.Listening.Short.Stories.html">A wealthy Englishman who can have anything he wants, finally encounters a woman he wants but can't have. </a></p>
      <p align="left" class="Summary1"><a href="ESL.English.Listening.Short.Stories/ESL.Listening.Short.Stories.html"><span class="style73">The desired woman is married to a husband who needs her - at least as long as he's alive. But for a man with money and no scruples, there's an obvious fix for that.</span></a></p>
